# Brewfile
# Written by Peter Hajas, first authored May 4, 2014

## Command-line utilities

### stow, the utility used for dotfiles
install stow

### tmux, for window management in the terminal
install tmux

### ctags, for code navigation
install ctags --HEAD

### wine, for Windows apps
install wine

## UI apps

### First, we need Cask. Cask is a way to install .apps using homebrew
install caskroom/cask/brew-cask

### Google Chrome
cask install google-chrome

### MacVim
cask install macvim

### Spotify
cask install spotify

### Bartender
cask install bartender

### f.lux
cask install flux

### Keyboard Maestro
cask install keyboard-maestro

### KeyRemap4Macbook
cask install keyremap4macbook

### Dropbox
cask install dropbox

### Slate
cask install slate

### Steam
cask install steam

### VLC
cask install vlc

### Audacity
cask install audacity

### TextExpander
cask install textexpander

### Sketch
cask install sketch

### Kaleidoscope
cask install kaleidoscope

### XQuartz
cask install xquartz

## Clean up Cask temporary files
cask cleanup

## Finally, update & doctor
update
doctor
